data.description: SAVE, SAVE, SAVE! FHA Assumable 6.625 rate with only 1% down!! Welcome to 10171 Bentley in North Royalton.  This beautiful 4 bedroom, 4 bath, warm and inviting colonial with an open floor plan is not to be missed.  It offers all the comfort and functionality needed for modern living. When you enter through the 2 story foyer you will immediately notice the light and airy feeling this house offers.  The first floor features hard wood floors throughout, with brand new Samsung stainless appliances in the heart of the home, the kitchen, with granite counters and stone back splash where your culinary creativity can be explored.  A dining room, office, morning room, first floor laundry with new washer and dryer and a half bath round out the first floor. The second floor includes 4 spacious bedrooms with the Owner's Suite boasting His and Hers walk in closets and glamour bath.  The lower level features a fifth bedroom, laundry room, full bath, and kitchen and state of the art media room and bar.  The back yard is private with it's covered outdoor kitchen with updated fridge and faucet and relaxing patio area.  Be sure to put 10171 Bentley at the very top of your viewing list where you can envision what this home may hold for you and your family. Includes built in office furniture, projector system and speakers in media room, and more.
